2010/11/1
Now, we have finished studying the basic git, and used git in two c files, TxtTools.c and FileNameTools.c. 

Next, we will do a practical task. I push a txt file "射雕英雄传"。 When you read it on you mobile phone, it's too big to load it into your cell phone memeory. 
you need to write a programe to split the txt file into some small txt files according to its content. 第一回风雪惊变 。。。 第二回江南七怪。。。。。The file name is section1.txt, section2.txt, section3.txt.......

Use the functions in the TxtTools.c and FileNameTools.c if it is possible. 

After finish this task, we will try more mobile phone programming. Hope you enjoy it. 

